kw.name: Assembly.Open Browser
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to given URL.

kw.name: Assembly.Wait Until Page Contains Element
kw.doc: Waits until element specified with `locator` appears on current page.

kw.name: Assembly.Source Should Match File
kw.doc: Diff the source of a page against the contents of a baseline file.

kw.name: Assembly.Capture Page Screenshot
kw.doc: Takes a screenshot of the current page and embeds it into the log.
